# Magnesium status and attention deficit hyperactivity disorder (ADHD)_ A meta-analysis
**Autores**: Mohammad Effatpanah
**Año**: 2018
**Journal**: Psychiatry Research, 274 (2019) 228-234. doi:10.1016/j.psychres.2019.02.043
**DOI/Link**: Magnesium; ADHD; Children; Adolescents; Meta-analysis; 

